# Git Workflow

Always follow the process in `prompt.ai/git_workflow.md`.

## Commit standards
Use Conventional Commits:

```text
<type>[optional scope]: <description>
```

Types:
- feat
- fix
- docs
- refactor
- test
- chore
- ci
- build
- perf
- style

## Basic rules
- Keep commits atomic and focused
- Avoid unrelated changes in the same commit
- Use clear, intentional commit messages
- Update `prompt.ai/development_log.md` with notable changes
